metadata.name: CHUMA HOLDINGS, INC.
metadata.description: Chuma Holdings, Inc. provides turnkey support services and finances loans to companies in legal cannabis industry in the United States. The company provides seed to sale business services, including funding and financing; compliance consulting and certification; dispensary and retail; commercial production and equipment build out; banking and payment processing; multichannel supply chain; branding, marketing, and sales; research and development; and consumer product solutions. Its support services include compliance consulting, security, management, bookkeeping, financial, real estate, equipment lending, tax planning, payroll, and human resource services. The company was formerly known as Cannamed Corporation and changed its name to Chuma Holdings, Inc. in August 2014. Chuma Holdings, Inc. is based in Chatsworth, California.
